\end_layout

\end_inset

Dominanza: sia 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{1}\left\{ \left(x_{1},x_{2}\right),\left(\pi_{1},1-\pi_{1}\right)'\right\} $
\end_inset

 e 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{2}\left\{ \left(x_{1},x_{2}\right),\left(\pi_{2},1-\pi_{2}\right)'\right\} $
\end_inset

.
 Se 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}\succ x_{2}$
\end_inset

, allora 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{1}\succ L_{2}$
\end_inset

 se e solo se 
\begin_inset Formula $\pi_{1}>\pi_{2}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

